sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant System
    
    Note over Player, System: UC-01: Place Object (Build Mode)
    Player->>System: selectObject(objectType)
    Player->>System: dragAndDrop(x, y)
    
    alt Target tile is empty & passable
        System->>System: validateTileEmpty(x, y)
        System->>System: update Map data structure
        System-->>Player: renderObjectAt(x, y)
    else Target tile is occupied
        System-->>Player: display visual warning (red highlight)
        System-->>Player: cancel placement (snap back to palette)
    end